  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "A squad of Catachan Jungle Fighters under hard-bitten Sergeant Greiss is dropped onto Rogar III to break an Ork incursion by stealth and decapitate the warband at its head. But Rogar III is a death world in the truest sense: its jungle is awake, evolving new horrors to drive the intruders out. Venom-maddened troopers turn on their comrades, hypnotic lights lure men into the dark, and the dead come walking back. Between the greenskins and a planet that wants them gone, Greiss, the trooper Lorenzo and the commissar's adjutant Braxton must finish the mission and find a way back out alive. A tense survival war story of soldiers fighting the ground beneath their boots.",
